{
  "stem": "10496.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this was not going to-- if we would have stayed in New York, we would have-- we would have fallen into-- into their way of life.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we wanted-- when we came to United States, we said we wanted it completely new.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In other words, I was looking for assimilation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and the-- my relatives over in New York were-- were back in the old days.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "19-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "February, 1942.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the last time--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--I saw her was in 1939.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, it was three years.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'39.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'40, '41.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "About two and a half years.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were-- it was quite a-- a reunion.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Went to--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, outside Boston.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Called Winthrop, Massachusetts.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and that's where I stayed for-- for the-- for the-- the next 10 years.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I had-- I know I had to learn the English language.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I made it my business to make sure I-- I-- I did learn.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had special-- well, special attention.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had a special teacher who taught me how to speak, how to get rid of my accent, and whatever.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was determined to--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1935.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Seven years.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Seven years.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it's just like-- the only education I got was basically real life experiences.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah-- oh, and chess.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first of all, I-- I had a sort of a rough beginning, because they put me in a-- I think the fifth grade, you know, where I should have been much higher.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I got some double promotions.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But still, I-- I graduated high school at age 20.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it didn't make any difference, because when I went to college I had a lot of students that were my age, you know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I'm always considered--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--the German refugee over in-- in-- in Winthrop, Massachusetts, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, they accepted me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Jewish population accepted me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the-- and I became very active, very quickly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I had some problems with the-- like the McLaughlin gang, you know, that they--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were a whole bunch of 12 to 13 cousins, and I guess they-- they didn't want any stranger, or they-- they thought I was a Nazi or something, you know.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they-- they gave me a hard time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I once remember I had to run for my life from those kids, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were kind of-- they were pretty rough.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they threw rocks at us and all that business-- at me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I had already made some friends.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they were in the same-- they had the same problem that I had because they were supporting me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right-- at that point, it was anti-German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think anti-- I was a-- I was-- you know, they were not-- probably not smart enough to realize that I was-- I was a Jew.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Here, too.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well,I knew it was--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a temporary situation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, once I-- I got away from-- from high school and into college, I met a lot of people that were concerned and-- and were sympathetic to my--to my-- way I feel, the way I thought and everything else.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the only thing I can say is that I was-- the-- the-- the poorest subject that I had in school [LAUGHS] was English.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I got bad grades in English.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everything else was fine, but English.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In other words, I was not concerned-- I never thought for a minute that I was going to end up in-- in the United States.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's-- that's what-- you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So you get-- you get an idea.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, high school-- I graduated high school 1948.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and I got good grades, by the way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I started getting good grades the-- the last four years-- 9th, 10th, 11th, 12th.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I was pretty good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I-- I had choices of colleges.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I thought the best thing-- best place to go was Tufts College--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--in Medford, Massachusetts.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was delighted.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was extremely happy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, thank goodness.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now-- you know, now I can start concentrating on-- on my life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Oh, absolutely.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, when-- when people made bonfires in-- in 1945?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was very, very delighted.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I became aware that many of my-- my-- my family didn't make it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In other words, as I said, about half of them did not make it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my-- my father had another brother, called Emil, who-- who did-- who ended up in a concentration camp, and I was very close to him.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And unfortunate.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Very unfortunate.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He-- he didn't make it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He ended up in-- in Eastern Europe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One of the camps in Eastern Europe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was very upset about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you know, life is for the living.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
